@janschulz, sorry this has taken so long to get around to.

I'm assume the reason you are (or were) having problems is because notifications are being fired when you use `setattr`. Given that, there really isn't a good public API for silent setting with Traitlets. So for now your best bet really is to use `instance_init`.

For a while the idea of a context manager called `mute_trait_notifications` (as opposed to `hold_trait_notifications`) was being considered, but it wasn't particularly popular. If silent setting in Traitlets is something you'd value, we could reopen that discussion.

