                {
                    "dtdId": "supplement/1",
                    "value": "<co-content><text>For those interested, the slides presented in the videos for this module can be downloaded here:  <a href=\"https://d396qusza40orc.cloudfront.net/phoenixassets/ml-foundations/intro.pdf\">intro.pdf</a></text></co-content>"
                }
            }
        ]
    }
}
```

To make this URL we need: 1. Course ID (`  "id": "qi9mnkIJEeWC4g7VhG4bTQ",`), 2. Element ID (`"id": "F1pTC",`)

Sometimes there are many PDFs to download on one page: `https://www.coursera.org/api/onDemandSupplements.v1/qi9mnkIJEeWC4g7VhG4bTQ~lVBJT?includes=asset&fields=openCourseAssets.v1%28typeName%29,openCourseAssets.v1%28definition%29`. In this case they are packed into one object:
