Nevermind, I solved the problem which was caused by me forgetting to consider the hierarchy of folders inside by `app.scss`. By putting this file in `/static` with the downloaded `foundation-sites` and setting its content like below: 

```sass
@import 'foundation-sites/scss/settings/_settings.scss';
@import 'foundation-sites/scss/foundation.scss';

@include foundation-everything;
```

